column5: Anyone fish gullrock yet??? Just curious.

I talked to a guy who fished Gullrock opening week. He stated that the walleyes were spawned out and the fishing was very good. Where are you staying. I'm headed to Golden Hook Camp on Gullrock tomorrow morning from MN.
Wal, Leaving for there tomorrow at 6:00a.m. sharp!!! We'll make sure to leave a few eaters for ya. Keep'er on the bottom! John

We are going June 7th to 5 lakes lodge. John, Thank you in advance for leaving a few. If you feel at all "guilty" for catching "too many" you can leave some of your left over beer with Everett. We will take care of it for you. Good luck. wal :cheers:
